Xuzhou RITMAN Equipment Co., Ltd. is an intelligent equipment enterprise under the Jiangsu Metavast group.

We are a galvanizing solution provider based in China, which offers turnkey projects of the eco-friendly, fully automated, and informationized hot-dip galvanizing plant, along with relevant training concerning the HDG plant, as well as renovating an old HDG plant into a modern one. 

The benefit of a fully automated and informationized or renovated modern HDG plant is the increase in production efficiency and the decrease in production-related consumption of zinc, electricity, gas, and water while maintaining the galvanizing quality.

The company is also SIEMENS's cooperation partner and has passed the certification of QMS and EMS.

Our company can offer relevant services and products as follows: 
Our services and products include:
 1. Consulting service regarding building or upgrading HDG plant;
 2. Design, manufacture and installation of a new HDG plant;
 3. Renovation of a traditional/old plant into a modern one; 
 4. EP Equipment, including: 
 a. Integrated Equipment for Rinsing Water
 b. Integrated Equipment for Flux Regeneration
 c. Galvanizing Fume Extraction and Treatment System
 d. Automatic Treatment Equipment for Waste Acid 
 e. Waste acid recycling plant
Our advantages: 
 1. Nearly 40 years of experience in galvanizing;
 2. 5 years of R&D in the galvanizing production line and relevant equipment;
 3. 30 patents and 29 software copyrights, and increasing;
 4. 80+ technical personnel from related fields;

